ActTerritorial Lands Act
SubjectWithdrawal from Disposal of Certain Tracts of Territorial Lands in the Northwest Territories (Dehcho Region) Order
PrecisWITHDRAWAL FROM DISPOSAL OF CERTAIN TRACTS OF TERRITORIAL LANDS IN THE NORTHWEST TERRITORIES (DEHCHO REGION) ORDER which withdraws from disposal the surface and subsurface rights of certain lands (approximately 54,708 square kilometers), in order to facilitate the settlement of Aboriginal land and resource agreements in the Northwest Territories.
